---
import BaseHead from '@components/BaseHead.astro';
import Blinkies from '@components/Blinkies.astro';
import Buttons from '@components/Buttons.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
import Navigation from '@components/Nav.astro';
import Stamps from '@components/Stamps.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '@src/consts';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={'Blinkies, Buttons, and Stamps'} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Navigation />
        <main>
            <article aria-label="Other Fun Stuff">
                <div class="sidebar content">
                    <h3>About Buttons, Stamps, and Blinkies</h3>
                    <p>I make buttons, stamps, and blinkies occassionally. Making them brings me joy! I also really like collecting them from old websites, especially the political blinkies. A reminder of another era! *sigh*</p>
                    <p>I hope you enjoy them too, as you may use them freely on your own website, as long as you don't claim them as your own. :) If you're feeling like you want to, wrap them in an <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> tag that links back to me at <a href="https://aristocraticarietta.neocities.org/">aristocraticarietta.neocities.org</a>!</p>
                    <p>Here's an example of what I mean (You can click on it to copy it to your clipboard!): </p>
                    <textarea 
                        id="link" 
                        readonly 
                        wrap="on" 
                        x-data 
                        @click="$el.select(); navigator.clipboard.writeText($el.value);"
                    >&lt;a href="https://aristocraticarietta.neocities.org/" target="_self" &gt;&lt;img src="https://aristocraticarietta.neocities.org/buttons/aristocraticarietta.png" alt=""&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</textarea>
                </div>
                <Buttons/>
                <Stamps/>
                <Blinkies/>
            </article>
            <section class="chat" aria-label="Chat & Guestbook">
                <iframe src="https://iframe.chat/embed?chat=AristocraticArietta" id="chattable"></iframe>
                <div class="sidebar guestbook">
                    <p><a href="https://aristocraticarietta.atabook.org/">Sign my guestbook!</a></p>
                    
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
<style>
    main {
        flex-direction: column-reverse;
    }
    article {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1em;
        width: 100%;
    }
    code {
        font-family: var(--font-sourcecodepro);
        background-color: var(--accent2);
        line-height: 1rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
    textarea {
        font: 1rem var(--font-sourcecodepro);
        resize: none;
        width: 100%;
        scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    #chattable {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 40vh;
        border-radius: var(--radius-glass);
        border: var(--border-glass);
    }
    .chat {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1em;
    }
    .content {
        padding: 0.5em;
    }
    p {
        width: 100%;
    }
    iframe {
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-glass);
    }
    @media (min-width: 1000px) {
        main {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }
        article {
            width: 75%;
        }
        textarea {
            width: 25%;
        }
        .content {
            flex-basis: 1;
        }
        .chat {
            flex-basis: 0;
        }
        #chattable {
            width: 20vw;
            height: 100%;
        }
	}
</style>

